sources.title: Amber's Descent | Full Movie | Psychological Horror Thriller | Kayla Stanton | Michael Mitton
sources.description:
Amber's Descent - After surviving a violent encounter, renowned pianist, Amber Waltz, relocates to a rural farmhouse to complete her latest symphony. When the music mysteriously begins writing itself, Amber slowly discovers that this piece could be her last.
2020.  Stars: Kayla Stanton, Michael Mitton, Don Knodel
